## Icon & Illustration Guidelines
- Use React components for custom SVGs
- Apply wobbly transforms: `transform: rotate(-2deg)`
- Vary stroke-width slightly for hand-drawn feel
- Use sketch color palette
- Add drop shadows sparingly

## Animation Guidelines
- Keep animations subtle and organic
- Prefer transforms over positional changes
- Use ease-in-out timing
- Typical duration: 150-300ms for interactions
- Flame effects: 2-3s infinite loops

